    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Dealing With D.S.L.</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Andrew Holliday letter on May 4 article lauds service he has gotten from small DSL provider</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I have had D.S.L. service for three months. Aside from a three-month delay between order and installation and one service failure, promptly solved by tech support, the service has been faultless. My provider is Flashcom-- you have a greater chance of success giving your dollars to small companies specializing in a new technology rather to than lumbering giants who just jumped on the bandwagon.</p>
        <p>ANDREW HOLLIDAY  New York</p>
      </block>
